longBusinessSummary: LIMES Schlosskliniken AG operates private hospitals for psychiatry, psychotherapy, and psychosomatics services. It focuses on the treatment of stress-related illnesses, as well as mental and emotional disorders, such as depression, acute burnout, affective disorders, and trauma. The company is headquartered in Cologne, Germany. LIMES Schlosskliniken AG is a subsidiary of G M F Capital Gmbh.
